<h1 id="toc0"><span>INTERNAL REFERENCE FILE</span></h1>
<h1 id="toc1"><span>ACCESS RESTRICTED TO CLEARANCE R/SSS OR HIGHER</span></h1>
<h4 id="toc2"><span>GLORY TO JALAKÅRA OF THE IMPENETRABLE, HOST AND BENEFACTOR TO MANKIND, NEVER SHALL THE ENDLESS WEAVE FRAY.</span></h4>
<h5 id="toc3"><span><em>YOU ARE WATCHED • YOU ARE PROTECTED • YOU ARE LOVED</em></span></h5>
</div>
